com.xilinx.rapidwright.design

Class SitePinInst

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.SitePinInst
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable

    public class SitePinInst
extends Object
implements Serializable, Cloneable
    This class represents the site pin sources and sinks in a physical net. These are target site pins for inter-site routing nets.
    See Also:
